<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0"/>
  <title>Employer Account - <%= status %></title>
  <style>
    body {
      background: #eef2f3;
      font-family: 'Arial', sans-serif;
      margin: 0;
      padding: 20px;
      color: #333;
    }
    .container {
      max-width: 600px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      background: #ffffff;
      border-radius: 10px;
      overflow: hidden;
      box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
      border: 1px solid #ddd;
      padding: 10px;
    }
    .header {
      background: linear-gradient(90deg, #1c92d2, #0072ff);
      padding: 25px;
      text-align: center;
      color: #fff;
      font-size: 24px;
      font-weight: bold;
      border-top-left-radius: 10px;
      border-top-right-radius: 10px;
    }
    .content {
      padding: 35px;
      font-size: 16px;
      line-height: 1.6;
    }
    .content strong {
      color: #0072ff;
    }
    .footer {
      background: #f4f7f9;
      padding: 15px;
      text-align: center;
      font-size: 12px;
      color: #888;
      border-top: 1px solid #e0e0e0;
      border-bottom-left-radius: 10px;
      border-bottom-right-radius: 10px;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="header">Job Portal</div>
    <div class="content">
      <p>Dear <%= firstName %>,</p>

      <% if (status === 'Approved') { %>
        <p>ðŸŽ‰ Congratulations! Your employer account has been <strong>approved</strong>.</p>
        <p>You can now log in and start posting jobs for free.</p>
      <% } else { %>
        <p>ðŸ˜” We're sorry to inform you that your employer account has been <strong>rejected</strong>.</p>
        <p>Please contact support if you believe this was in error.</p>
      <% } %>

      <p>Thanks for joining us!</p>
      <p>Best regards,<br/> Job Portal Team</p>
    </div>
    <div class="footer">
      &copy; <%= new Date().getFullYear() %> Job Portal. All rights reserved.
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
